d.'=>'Contact Form 7 從 %2$s 版開始，%1$s 勾點<strong>已淘汰不用</strong> ，請改用 %3$s。','Flamingo'=>'Flamingo','Install a message storage plugin before this happens to you. %s saves all messages through contact forms into the database. Flamingo is a free WordPress plugin created by the same author as Contact Form 7.'=>'在發生這種狀況前，請為這個網站安裝個能夠儲存電子郵件的外掛。Flamingo 是由 Contact Form 7 開發者 Takayuki Miyoshi 所開發的免費 WordPress 外掛，%s 可直接透過聯絡表單將所有電子郵件儲存到資料庫中。','Contact Form 7 does not store submitted messages anywhere. Therefore, you may lose important messages forever if your mail server has issues or you make a mistake in mail configuration.'=>'Contact Form 7 不會儲存已傳送的電子郵件，所以當電子郵件伺服器發生問題或電子郵件設定有了錯誤，便可能永久失去重要電子郵件。','Before you cry over spilt mail&#8230;'=>'在為錯發的電子郵件後悔之前...','https://contactform7.com/comment-blacklist/'=>'https://contactform7.com/comment-blacklist/','Contact Form 7 supports spam-filtering with %1$s. Intelligent %2$s blocks annoying spambots. Plus, using %3$s, you can block messages containing specified keywords or those sent from specified IP addresses.'=>'Contact Form 7 支援 %1$s 進行垃圾訊息篩選，而智慧型 %2$s 可封鎖惱人的垃圾訊息機器人。除此之外，使用%3$s可以阻止包含特定關鍵字或從特定 IP 位址傳送的電子郵件。','Spammers target everything; your contact forms are not an exception. Before you get spammed, protect your contact forms with the powerful anti-spam features Contact Form 7 provides.'=>'垃圾訊息業者不會放過任何目標，這個網站的聯絡表單也不例外。請在網站收到垃圾訊息前，使用 Contact Form 7 所提供的強大反垃圾訊息功能保護聯絡表單。','Getting spammed? You have protection.'=>'收到垃圾訊息？保護網站的完整解決方案就在這裡。','Multiple form controls are in a single label element.'=>'單一標籤元素中包含多個表單控制項。','FAQ about Configuration Validator'=>'組態驗證程式的常見問題集','https://contactform7.com/configuration-validator-faq/'=>'https://contactform7.com/configuration-validator-faq/','The answer to the quiz is incorrect.'=>'問答題的答案不正確。','There was an error uploading the file.'=>'上傳檔案時發生錯誤。','You are not allowed to upload files of this type.'=>'目前的登入身分沒有上傳這個檔案類型的權限。','There was an unknown error uploading the file.'=>'上傳檔案時發生未知錯誤。','You must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.'=>'傳送電子郵件前，你必須接受條款及條件。','One or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.'=>'一個或多個欄位發生錯誤。請檢查並重試。','There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.'=>'嘗試傳送電子郵件時發生錯誤。請稍後再試。','Thank you for your message. It has been sent.'=>'感謝你的留言，已將留言傳送給站務人員。','mail subject%1$s "%2$s"'=>'%2$s (由《%1$s》的聯絡表單傳送)','Misconfiguration leads to mail delivery failure or other troubles. Validate your contact forms now.'=>'組態錯誤會導致電子郵件傳送失敗或其他問題，請立即驗證這個網站的聯絡表單。','Validate Contact Form 7 Configuration'=>'驗證 Contact Form 7 的聯絡表單組態','https://contactform7.com/configuration-errors/'=>'https://contactform7.com/configuration-errors/','Configuration validation completed. No invalid contact form was found.'=>'已完成設定驗證，沒有無效的聯絡表單。','Configuration validation completed. %s invalid contact form was found.'=>'已完成設定驗證，找到 %s 份無效的聯絡表單。','Validate Configuration'=>'驗證組態','Validate %s contact form now'=>'立即驗證 %s 份聯絡表單','You are not allowed to validate configuration.'=>'目前的登入身分沒有驗證組態的權限。','https://contactform7.com/recaptcha/'=>'https://contactform7.com/recaptcha/','Secret Key'=>'密鑰','Site Key'=>'網站金鑰','Settings saved.'=>'設定已儲存。','Invalid key values.'=>'無效的金鑰。','reCAPTCHA'=>'reCAPTCHA','CAPTCHA (Really Simple CAPTCHA)'=>'CAPTCHA 驗證 (Really Simple CAPTCHA)','https://ideasilo.wordpress.com/'=>'https://ideasilo.wordpress.com/','Takayuki Miyoshi'=>'Takayuki Miyoshi','Just another contact form plugin. Simple but flexible.'=>'簡單靈活的聯絡表單外掛。','https://contactform7.com/'=>'https://contactform7.com/','Contact form %d'=>'聯絡表單 %d','Generate a form-tag for a multi-line text input field. For more details, see %s.'=>'為多行文字輸入欄位產生表單標籤。如需進一步了解，請參閱〈%s〉。','text area'=>'文字區域','This field requires author\'s URL'=>'填表者的網址在這個表單欄位中為必填','This field requires author\'s email address'=>'填表者的電子郵件地址在這個表單欄位中為必填','This field requires author\'s name'=>'填表者的名字在這個表單欄位中為必填','Akismet'=>'Akismet','Text fields'=>'文字欄位','https://contactform7.com/text-fields/'=>'https://contactform7.com/text-fields/','Generate a form-tag for a single-line telephone number input field. For more details, see %s.'=>'為單行電話號碼輸入欄位產生表單標籤。如需進一步了解，請參閱〈%s〉。','Generate a form-tag for a single-line URL input field. For more details, see %s.'=>'為單行網址輸入欄位產生表單標籤。如需進一步了解，請參閱〈%s〉。','Generate a form-tag for a single-line email address input field. For more details, see %s.'=>'為單行電子郵件地址輸入欄位產生表單標籤。如需進一步了解，請參閱〈%s〉。','Generate a form-tag for a single-line plain text input field. For more details, see %s.'=>'為單行純文字輸入欄位產生表單標籤。如需進一步了解，請參閱〈%s〉。','tel'=>'電話號碼','URL'=>'網址','email'=>'電子郵件地址','text'=>'文字','Telephone number that the sender entered is invalid'=>'寄件者輸入了無效的電話號碼','URL that the sender entered is invalid'=>'寄件者輸入了無效的連結','Email address that the sender entered is invalid'=>'寄件者輸入了無效的電子郵件地址','Label'=>'按鈕文字','Submit button'=>'傳送按鈕','https://contactform7.com/submit-button/'=>'https://contactform7.com/submit-button/','Generate a form-tag for a submit button. For more details, see %s.'=>'為傳送按鈕產生表單標籤。如需進一步了解，請參閱〈%s〉。','submit'=>'傳送按鈕','Insert a blank item as the first option'=>'以空白項目作為第一個選項','Allow multiple selections'=>'允許多重選取','Generate a form-tag for a drop-down menu. For more details, see %s.'=>'為下拉式選單產生表單標籤。如需進一步了解，請參閱〈%s〉。','drop-down menu'=>'下拉式選單','One pipe-separated question-answer pair (e.g. The capital of Brazil?|Rio) per line.'=>'每行一組問題及答案，問題及答案以直立線符號 | 進行分隔 (例如: 巴西的首都是哪個城市？|里約熱內盧)。','Questions and answers'=>'問題及答案','Quiz'=>'問答題','https://contactform7.com/quiz/'=>'https://contactform7.com/quiz/','Generate a form-tag for a question-answer pair. For more details, see %s.'=>'為問答題產生表單標籤。如需進一步了解，請參閱〈%s〉。','quiz'=>'問答題','Sender does not enter the correct answer to the quiz'=>'寄件者並未輸入問答題的正確答案','Slider'=>'滑桿','Spinbox'=>'微調方塊','Number fields'=>'數值欄位','https://contactform7.com/number-fields/'=>'https://contactform7.com/number-fields/','Generate a form-tag for a field for numeric value input. For more details, see %s.'=>'為數值輸入欄位產生表單標籤。如需進一步了解，請參閱〈%s〉。','number'=>'數值','Number is larger than maximum limit'=>'數值高於最大值限制','Number is smaller than minimum limit'=>'數值低於最小值限制','Number format that the sender entered is invalid'=>'寄件者輸入了無效的數值格式','This contact form has file uploading fields, but the temporary folder for the files (%s) does not exist or is not writable. You can create the folder or change its permission manually.'=>'這份聯絡表單中包含了檔案上傳欄位，但是檔案的暫存資料夾 (%s) 不存在或無法寫入。請手動建立資料夾或修改資料夾權限設定以修正這個問題。','To attach the file uploaded through this field to mail, you need to insert the corresponding mail-tag (%s) into the File Attachments field on the Mail tab.'=>'要在電子郵件中附加這個上傳的檔案，必須將對應的電子郵件標籤 %s 插入 [電子郵件] 分頁中的 [檔案附件] 欄位。','Acceptable file types'=>'可接受的檔案類型','File size limit (bytes)'=>'檔案大小限制 (單位為 Byte，即位元組)','File uploading and attachment'=>'檔案上傳及附件','https://contactform7.com/file-uploading-and-attachment/'=>'https://contactform7.com/file-uploading-and-attachment/','Generate a form-tag for a file uploading field. For more details, see %s.'=>'為檔案上傳欄位產生表單標籤。如需進一步了解，請參閱〈%s〉。','file'=>'檔案上傳','Uploading a file fails for PHP error'=>'因 PHP 錯誤導致上傳失敗','Uploaded file is too large'=>'上傳的檔案大小超過上限','Uploaded file is not allowed for file type'=>'系統不接受上傳檔案的檔案類型','Uploading a file fails for any reason'=>'因不明原因導致上傳失敗','Max'=>'最大值','Min'=>'最小值','Range'=>'範圍','Use this text as the placeholder of the field'=>'使用預設值作為這個表單欄位的示範內容','Default value'=>'預設值','Date field'=>'日期欄位','https://contactform7.com/date-field/'=>'https://contactform7.com/date-field/','Generate a form-tag for a date input field. For more details, see %s.'=>'為日期輸入欄位產生表單標籤。如需進一步了解，請參閱〈%s〉。','date'=>'日期','Date is later than maximum limit'=>'日期晚於最大值限制','Date is earlier than minimum limit'=>'日期早於最小值限制','Date format that the sender entered is invalid'=>'寄件者輸入了無效的日期格式','To use the value input through this field in a mail field, you need to insert the corresponding mail-tag (%s) into the field on the Mail tab.'=>'要在電子郵件中導入這個表單欄位的值，必須將對應的電子郵件標籤 %s 插入 [電子郵件] 分頁中的欄位。','Make checkboxes exclusive'=>'將核取方塊變更為單選按鈕','Wrap each item with label element'=>'將 label 元素套用至選項文字','Put a label first, a checkbox last'=>'選項文字在前，選項功能在後','One option per line.'=>'每行一個選項。','Required field'=>'必填欄位','Field type'=>'欄位類型','Checkboxes, radio buttons and menus'=>'核取方塊、選項按鈕及選單','https://contactform7.com/checkboxes-radio-buttons-and-menus/'=>'https://contactform7.com/checkboxes-radio-buttons-and-menus/','Generate a form-tag for a group of radio buttons. For more details, see %s.'=>'為一組選項按鈕產生表單標籤。如需進一步了解，請參閱〈%s〉。','Generate a form-tag for a group of checkboxes. For more details, see %s.'=>'為一組核取方塊產生表單標籤。如需進一步了解，請參閱〈%s〉。','radio buttons'=>'選項按鈕','checkboxes'=>'核取方塊','This contact form contains CAPTCHA fields, but the necessary libraries (GD and FreeType) are not available on your server.'=>'這份聯絡表單中使用了 CAPTCHA 驗證欄位，但這個網站的伺服器並未提供必要的 GD 以及 FreeType 函式庫。','This contact form contains CAPTCHA fields, but the temporary folder for the files (%s) does not exist or is not writable. You can create the folder or change its permission manually.'=>'這份聯絡表單中使用了 CAPTCHA 驗證欄位，但是檔案的暫存資料夾 (%s) 不存在或無法寫入。請透過手動建立資料夾或修改資料夾權限設定以修正這個問題。','Input field settings'=>'設定輸入欄位','Image settings'=>'圖片設定','https://contactform7.com/captcha/'=>'https://contactform7.com/captcha/','Generate form-tags for a CAPTCHA image and corresponding response input field. For more details, see %s.'=>'為 CAPTCHA 驗證圖片及其對應的回應輸入欄位產生表單標籤。如需進一步了解，請參閱〈%s〉。','To use CAPTCHA, you first need to install and activate %s plugin.'=>'如需使用 CAPTCHA 驗證功能，請先安裝並啟用 %s 外掛。','CAPTCHA'=>'CAPTCHA 驗證','Your entered code is incorrect.'=>'目前輸入的認證碼不正確。','The code that sender entered does not match the CAPTCHA'=>'寄信者輸入的驗證碼與 CAPTCHA 提供的不相符','Insert Tag'=>'插入標籤','Class attribute'=>'類別屬性','Id attribute'=>'ID 屬性','Options'=>'選項','Name'=>'欄位名稱','Acceptance checkbox'=>'同意方式核取方塊','https://contactform7.com/acceptance-checkbox/'=>'https://contactform7.com/acceptance-checkbox/','Generate a form-tag for an acceptance checkbox. For more details, see %s.'=>'為同意方式核取方塊產生表單標籤。如需進一步了解，請參閱〈%s〉。','acceptance'=>'同意方式','<code>%1$s</code> property of a <code>WPCF7_ContactForm</code> object is <strong>no longer accessible</strong>. Use <code>%2$s</code> method instead.'=>'<strong>無法存取</strong> <code>WPCF7_ContactForm</code> 物件 <strong> 的 <code>%1$s</code> 屬性。請改用 <code>%2$s</code> 方法加以取代。','Untitled'=>'未命名','Contact Form'=>'聯絡表單','There is a field with input that is shorter than the minimum allowed length'=>'當輸入的字元長度低於預設值時','There is a field with input that is longer than the maximum allowed length'=>'當輸入的字元長度高於預設值時','There is a field that the sender must fill in'=>'當寄件者未填寫必填欄位時','There are terms that the sender must accept'=>'當寄件者必須接受相關條款時','Submission was referred to as spam'=>'系統判定送出的內容為垃圾郵件','Validation errors occurred'=>'發生驗證錯誤','Sender\'s message failed to send'=>'寄件者的電子郵件傳送失敗','Sender\'s message was sent successfully'=>'寄件者的電子郵件傳送成功','Message Body:'=>'電子郵件內文:','Subject: %s'=>'主旨: %s','From: %s'=>'寄件者: %s','Send'=>'傳送','Your message'=>'你的訊息','Your email'=>'你的電子郵件地址','Your name'=>'你的全名','Form-tag Generator: %s'=>'表單標籤產生程式: %s','For more information:'=>'進一步了解相關資訊:','Any information you provide will not be shared with service providers without your authorization.'=>'網站管理員所提供的任何資訊，未經當事人授權，不會分享給服務提供商。','You may need to first sign up for an account with the service that you plan to use. When you do so, you would need to authorize Contact Form 7 to access the service with your account.'=>'網站管理員必須先向計畫採用的服務註冊一個帳號。註冊成功後，請授權 Contact Form 7 以網站管理員的帳號存取該項服務。','On this screen, you can manage services that are available through Contact Form 7. Using API will allow you to collaborate with any services that are available.'=>'在這個畫面中，網站管理員可以透過 Contact Form 7 管理可用的服務。使用 API 可讓這個網站與任何可用的服務進行協同作業。','There are also special mail-tags that have specific names, but do not have corresponding form-tags. They are used to represent meta information of form submissions like the submitter&#8217;s IP address or the URL of the page.'=>'有些含有指定名稱的特殊電子郵件標籤，並沒有對應的表單標籤。這些特殊電子郵件標籤用於顯示傳送表單的中繼資訊，例如傳送表單的使用者的 IP 位址或頁面網址。','A mail-tag is also a short code enclosed in square brackets that you can use in every Mail and Mail (2) field. A mail-tag represents a user input value through an input field of a corresponding form-tag.'=>'電子郵件標籤就是用於 [電子郵件] 及 [電子郵件 (2)] 各個欄位中以方括弧括住的短代碼。電子郵件標籤透過對應的表單標籤輸入欄位，將使用者輸入的值顯示出來。','While form-tags have a comparatively complex syntax, you do not need to know the syntax to add form-tags because you can use the straightforward tag generator (<strong>Generate Tag</strong> button on this screen).'=>'雖然表單標籤具備相對複雜的語法，但製表者無須掌握新增表單標籤的語法，便可以透過簡單易用的標籤產生程式產生表單標籤。在這個畫面上，那一整列的按鈕代表不同類型的<strong>表單標籤產生程式</strong>。','A form-tag is a short code enclosed in square brackets used in a form content. A form-tag generally represents an input field, and its components can be separated into four parts: type, name, options, and values. Contact Form 7 supports several types of form-tags including text fields, number fields, date fields, checkboxes, radio buttons, menus, file-uploading fields, CAPTCHAs, and quiz fields.'=>'表單標籤就是用於表單內容中以方括弧括住的短代碼。表單標籤一般顯示為輸入欄位，其構成分為四個部分: 類型、名稱、選項及欄位的值。Contact Form 7 支援各種類型的表單標籤，包含文字欄位、數值欄位、日期欄位、核取方塊、選項按鈕、選單、檔案上傳欄位、CAPTCHA 驗證以及問答題欄位。','<strong>Additional Settings</strong> provides a place where you can customize the behavior of this contact form by adding code snippets.'=>'<strong>[其他設定]</strong> 提供了一個可以讓製表者新增程式碼片段以便自訂聯絡表單行為的欄位。','In <strong>Messages</strong>, you can edit various types of messages used for this contact form. These messages are relatively short messages, like a validation error message you see when you leave a required field blank.'=>'在 <strong>[訊息]</strong> 設定頁中，可以編輯用於該份聯絡表單的各項訊息。這些都是相對較短的訊息，類似使用者在必填欄位留空時看到的驗證錯誤訊息。','<strong>Mail (2)</strong> is an additional mail template that works similar to Mail. Mail (2) is different in that it is sent only when Mail has been sent successfully.'=>'<strong>[電子郵件 (2)]</strong> 是與 [電子郵件] 運作方式相仿的電子郵件範本。[電子郵件 (2)] 的不同處在於它只有在 [電子郵件] 範本的內容傳送成功後，才會進行傳送。','<strong>Mail</strong> manages a mail template (headers and message body) that this contact form will send when users submit it. You can use Contact Form 7&#8217;s mail-tags here.'=>'在 <strong>[電子郵件]</strong> 設定頁中，可管理使用者傳送表單後，聯絡表單會寄送給收件者的電子郵件範本 (即電子郵件標頭及內文)。製表者也可以在這裡使用 Contact Form 7 的電子郵件標籤。','<strong>Form</strong> is a content of HTML form. You can use arbitrary HTML, which is allowed inside a form element. You can also use Contact Form 7&#8217;s form-tags here.'=>'<strong>[表單]</strong> 設定頁儲存了 HTML 表單的內容。在這個設定頁中，製表者可以使用所有可用於 form 元素的 HTML 標籤，也可以使用 Contact Form 7 的表單標籤。','<strong>Title</strong> is the title of a contact form. This title is only used for labeling a contact form, and can be edited.'=>'<strong>[表單標題]</strong> 就是聯絡表單的標題。表單標題僅用於標示聯絡表單，且可隨時進行編輯。','On this screen, you can edit a contact form. A contact form is comprised of the following components:'=>'在這個畫面中，製表者可以編輯聯絡表單。每份聯絡表單均由以下項目所組成:','<strong>Duplicate</strong> - Clones that contact form. A cloned contact form inherits all content from the original, but has a different ID.'=>'<strong>[複製]</strong> 功能 - 複製聯絡表單。複製出來的聯絡表單包含了來源聯絡表單的所有內容，僅有表單 ID 不同。','<strong>Edit</strong> - Navigates to the editing screen for that contact form. You can also reach that screen by clicking on the contact form title.'=>'<strong>[編輯]</strong> 功能 - 瀏覽至聯絡表單的編輯畫面。製表者也可以點擊聯絡表單的標題進入編輯畫面。','Hovering over a row in the contact forms list will display action links that allow you to manage your contact form. You can perform the following actions:'=>'將游標停駐於聯絡表單清單任一列上，便會顯示管理聯絡表單的操作連結。製表者可以進行以下操作:','On this screen, you can manage contact forms provided by Contact Form 7. You can manage an unlimited number of contact forms. Each contact form has a unique ID and Contact Form 7 shortcode ([contact-form-7 ...]). To insert a contact form into a post or a text widget, insert the shortcode into the target.'=>'在這個畫面中，可以管理 Contact Form 7 所提供的聯絡表單，且無管理數量限制。每份聯絡表單均包含唯一 ID 及 Contact Form 7 短代碼 ([contact-form-7 ...])。如需在文章或文字小工具中插入聯絡表單，將對應的短代碼插入適當位置即可。','Mail-tags'=>'電子郵件標籤','Form-tags'=>'表單標籤','Available Actions'=>'可進行的操作','Overview'=>'概觀','You can add customization code snippets here. For details, see %s.'=>'請在這裡新增自訂程式碼片段。如需詳細資訊，請參閱〈%s〉。','https://contactform7.com/additional-settings/'=>'https://contactform7.com/additional-settings/','File attachments'=>'檔案附件','Use HTML content type'=>'使用 HTML 內容類型','Exclude lines with blank mail-tags from output'=>'在輸出內容中排除含有無內容電子郵件標籤的那一行','Message body'=>'電子郵件內文','Additional headers'=>'其他標頭','Subject'=>'主旨','From'=>'寄件者','To'=>'收件者','In the following fields, you can use these mail-tags:'=>'在下方欄位中，可以使用以下電子郵件標籤:','Mail (2) is an additional mail template often used as an autoresponder.'=>'[電子郵件 (2)] 是另一個電子郵件範本，通常用於自動回覆指定訊息給送出表單的使用者。','Use Mail (2)'=>'使用 [電子郵件 (2)]','Mail (2)'=>'電子郵件 (2)','Y/m/d'=>'Y/n/j','Edit &#8220;%s&#8221;'=>'編輯〈%s〉','Edit'=>'編輯','Date'=>'日期','Author'=>'製表者','Shortcode'=>'短代碼','Title'=>'表單標題','Additional Settings'=>'其他設定','Additional Settings (%d)'=>'其他設定 (%d)','Messages'=>'訊息','Mail'=>'電子郵件','Form'=>'表單','Support'=>'技術支援','https://contactform7.com/support/'=>'https://contactform7.com/support/','FAQ'=>'常見問題集','https://contactform7.com/faq/'=>'https://contactform7.com/faq/','Docs'=>'線上說明文件','https://contactform7.com/docs/'=>'https://contactform7.com/docs/','You are about to delete this contact form.
  \'Cancel\' to stop, \'OK\' to delete.'=>'即將刪除這份聯絡表單。
點擊 [取消] 以停止操作，點擊 [確定] 以刪除。','Delete'=>'刪除','Duplicate'=>'複製','Status'=>'狀態','You can also use this old-style shortcode:'=>'同時也可以使用舊式短代碼:','Copy this shortcode and paste it into your post, page, or text widget content:'=>'將下方的短代碼複製至這個網站的文章、頁面或文字小工具中:','Enter title here'=>'請在這裡輸入聯絡表單標題','Save'=>'儲存','You are not allowed to edit this contact form.'=>'目前的登入身分沒有編輯這份聯絡表單的權限。','https://contactform7.com/save-submitted-messages-with-flamingo/'=>'https://contactform7.com/save-submitted-messages-with-flamingo/','Spam filtering with Akismet'=>'使用 Akismet 篩選垃圾訊息','https://contactform7.com/spam-filtering-with-akismet/'=>'https://contactform7.com/spam-filtering-with-akismet/','Setting up mail'=>'設定電子郵件','https://contactform7.com/setting-up-mail/'=>'https://contactform7.com/setting-up-mail/','https://contactform7.com/donate/'=>'https://contactform7.com/donate/','Contact Form 7 needs your support.'=>'Contact Form 7 需要你的支持。','Dismiss'=>'關閉','<strong>Contact Form 7 %1$s requires WordPress %2$s or higher.</strong> Please <a href="%3$s">update WordPress</a> first.'=>'<strong>Contact Form 7 %1$s 版需要 WordPress %2$s 版或更新版本</strong>，請先<a href="%3$s">更新 WordPress</a>。','Settings'=>'設定','Contact form deleted.'=>'聯絡表單已刪除。','Contact form saved.'=>'聯絡表單已儲存。','Contact form created.'=>'聯絡表單已建立。','Search Contact Forms'=>'搜尋聯絡表單','Search results for &#8220;%s&#8221;'=>'「%s」的搜尋結果','The changes you made will be lost if you navigate away from this page.'=>'如果離開這個頁面，便會失去之前所做的全部變更。','Error in deleting.'=>'刪除時發生錯誤。','You are not allowed to delete this item.'=>'目前的登入身分沒有刪除這個項目的權限。','You are not allowed to edit this item.'=>'目前的登入身分沒有編輯這個項目的權限。','Integration'=>'整合','Add New'=>'新增聯絡表單','Add New Contact Form'=>'新增聯絡表單','Contact Forms'=>'聯絡表單','Edit Contact Form'=>'編輯聯絡表單','Contact'=>'聯絡表單','Contact Form 7'=>'Contact Form 7']];